ative' style='margin-right: 12px;'>-$40.00</span>\n      \" & btnDrain & \"\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <br>\n  <div class='cmd-row' style='margin-top: 8px;'>\n    <span>= REMAINING SAVINGS:</span>\n    <span id='eos-total' style='color: #00ff66; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;'>$\" & TotalSavings & \"</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style='text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;'>\n    <button id='eos-proceed' class='cmd-btn'>[ PROCEED ]</button>\n  </div>\""
